        <dcterms:description rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#HTML">The SI unit of volume, equal to 1.0e6 cm3, 1000 liters, 35.3147 ft3, or 1.30795 yd3. A cubic meter holds about 264.17 U.S. liquid gallons or 219.99 British Imperial gallons.</dcterms:description>
